data.description: Freshly updated home now ready for you in established neighborhood with no HOA. This one story home on nearly a 1/4 acre lot has had the foundation leveled (with transferrable warranty), new interior paint top to bottom (no more popcorn ceilings), new canless lighting, new cabinet hardware, new granite countertops and new faucet fixtures in kitchen and both bathrooms, new garage doors with new openers, and beautiful new vinyl plank flooring running throughout the home (no carpet!) gives it a large open feeling. In the kitchen you can enjoy brand new stainless appliances. Home has wood burning fireplace and built in bookshelves in living and separate space for dining. Double doors to the backyard and covered patio, storage building conveys. Close convenience to shopping and nearby Kraft park, NBISD. Ask about seller contributions for foundation warranty transfer and home warranty!
